onClick:
{{ 
storeValue(
  "duplicatePromptText",
  `
⚠️ Duplicate Email Records Detected

• Duplicate Messages: ${appsmith.store.duplicateCount || 0}
• Unique Messages: ${appsmith.store.duplicateUniqueLogs?.length || 0}
• Total Messages to Send: ${(appsmith.store.duplicateUniqueLogs?.length || 0) + (appsmith.store.duplicateCount || 0)}

Batch Details:
• Payment Type: ${Dropdown1.selectedOptionValue}
• Original Batch Ref: ${appsmith.store.currentBatchRef}
• Template: ${appsmith.store.currentTemplateName || "Unknown"}

Admin:
• ${appsmith.user.email}

What will happen:
• Duplicate messages will be assigned new unique hashes.
• A new batch will be created for this resend.
• Emails will be queued as a new job.

⚠️ Warning:
Resending duplicates may cause recipients to receive repeated emails.
This action cannot be undone.

Do you want to continue?
`
).then(() => showModal("ModalConfirmDuplicate"))
}}
